text: André Lamy (born 29 August 1932) is a French wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman middleweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:French male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of France Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Puy-de-Dôme
